<HistoricalDocument xmlns="http://example.com/historicaldocument">
  <Metadata>
    <Language>German</Language>
    <WritingDirection>ltr</WritingDirection>
    <PhysicalDescription>Parchment, 1 folio side, good condition.</PhysicalDescription>
    <Description>Excerpt from a historical German manuscript, likely a chronicle or religious text.</Description>
    <Script>Latin</Script>
  </Metadata>
  <Page>
    <Body>
      <MarginalNote placement="left_margin">
        <Line>Muran</Line>
        <Line>glas</Line>
        <Line>Süttin</Line>
      </MarginalNote>
      <Paragraph>
        <Line><Initial type="simple">Z</Initial>elbs im frowaltar die sohend</Line>
        <Line>wir gancz vnd ein stuck von</Line>
        <Line>dem heiligen frow crütz dz</Line>
        <Line>lit ir brust vnd ein</Line>
        <Line>bein von sant marien madalene</Line>
        <Line>ruggrot jch vff samstag noch</Line>
        <Line>dem ostertag der do was der</Line>
        <Line>ander tag des abrellas do</Line>
        <Line>furend wir gon meran do</Line>
        <Line>ligend in sant <Emphasis type="underline">P</Emphasis>steffans</Line>
        <Line>kirchen bi hundert der kindlin</Line>
        <Line>die herodes erschlug in einem</Line>
        <Line>altar die sohend wir vnd</Line>
        <Line>sicht man noch bescheidenlich</Line>
        <Line>ir hand vnd füs vnd die</Line>
        <Line>nagel dar an <Emphasis type="underline">M</Emphasis>erines an</Line>
        <Line>dem sūnentag früg do</Line>
      </Paragraph>
    </Body>
  </Page>
</HistoricalDocument>
